---
title: One-Pot Jambalaya-Inspired Chicken with Tomato Rice
description: Jambalaya is famous in New Orleans for its ability to pack serious smoky flavours into one colourful pot of rice. Our rendition is popping with green bell peppers, onions, garlic, tomato and chicken.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-jambalaya-inspired-chicken-770aefc3.jpg
